snippet: More than 200 migrants from Myanmar who are being held in southern Thailand will be pushed back out to sea, the police said Monday.
lead_paragraph: More than 200 migrants from Myanmar who are being held in southern Thailand will be pushed back out to sea, the police said Monday.

headline.main: Thailand: Police to Send Migrants Back Out to Sea in Boats
